<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE HANDWRITING ON THE WALL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Belshazar guolvakna ah,
 A lawite mi sangkhat tawh;
 Nun nawpna zu a dawn lai un
 Thudik Bu-a zik guolin;
 Nunnuoma a um laiun,
 Lal In lopi tak sungah;
 Maksan lauhna'n a hung dim tau,
 Ziechuh banga khut ahi.

[V2]
 Banga chuh Pathien khut ahi! (2)
 &quot;Na ting puoi!&quot; ti'n zik ahi dem?
 &quot;Ginum!&quot; ti'n ahi zaw dem?
 Banga chu khutin a zik laiin.

[V3]
 2. Enin, sal hangsan Daniel,
 Mipite ma a dingin;
 Lal chapo chuh a hilhgaih a,
 A thil hihkhelh haw ziekin;
 Thudik chuh a simdawka
 Mi cheng sietna ding thu chuh,
 &quot;Tu'n Lalgam chuh a bei eitai&quot;
 Banga khut zik chun a tii.

[V4]
 3. Thildik hih dinga ginna,
 Gunchuhna leh hansanna;
 Thagau in Daniel a piek chuh,
 A hatna thuguk ahi;
 Judia gama a In leh,
 Sal a hihna mun ale;
 A Pathien in banga A zik!
 Chuh chien takin a hethei.

[V5]
 4. I thilhih hawu tiemteh ahi,
 Khut khatin a zik zing;
 Migilo, na lung Isu pie'n,
 A Lal thupieka khunin;
 A ni chuh a hung nai tai,
 Mitin, chungah tung intin;
 Migilo thiemloh chansakna,
 Bang achun kizik ina!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>156</hymn_number>
</song>